reviewText: Probably would have been a much higher review, but out of the three vhs tapes in the collection, there were only two sent.  One was the jacket, but no vhs tape in it!  I tried e-mailing the seller - no luck - never heard from him.  So, I only got 2/3 of what I paid for!!!

Can never go wrong with Doris Day! Yes, I still have a VHS player and it was quality condition.
Still watch a few times a month.
Loved all three of these movies.  Whenever I need a pick me up, I play one of these movies.  They put me in a great mood.
